  "duration": 179.730000768,
  "text": " At Brex, we're building all-in-one finance for the next generation of businesses. We do corporate cards, business accounts, expense management, and bill pay. We're the leading technology companies in the world. One macro trend in financial services as a whole is the importance of user experience that was not previously valued. And what we're really trying to do with this is make it so that businesses can manage all their finance in one space and provide premium features that users can leverage to make that even better. BillPay is one piece of that under Brex Premium that allows users to manage and pay their bills all in one place. One of the biggest issues we saw of the market was the reliability on financial software. If you uploaded a receipt or if you uploaded a bill, how reliable could you be that information was actually correct. Because if it wasn't correct, you would have to verify it and retype it anyway. And it was really hard to actually find that in the market because you only found traditional CR players that would just do it with some speed, but probably like low accuracy. And that wasn't enough. When we were looking for a document processing solution, we were looking for something that one would provide really high accuracy, the second is low latency, And third it really about a solution that can be customizable to what we want And I think this is where SCALE really excels is that they have a whole team of AI and ML experts that can customize our model and solution to exactly our feedback and what we want out of it. Originally, we actually didn't pick Scale as our original vendor, and that was a big mistake. We went with another vendor, and the accuracy and the speed wasn't good enough. And as soon as we switched to Scale, it increased dramatically. So I kind of regret not going with it in the first place. The collaboration process with SCALE has really been a breath of fresh air. We want to achieve our mission as fast as possible. And in areas where we're not able to invest internally in the best, we want to work with the best. And SCALE.AI has helped us fill that need. Just to quantify it, for example, we have lowered and I think two seconds response time and 99.9% accuracy, which is unheard of in our industry. Now that we've had this amazing experience of scale document on our bill pay product, we want to use it for any other type of document processing that we have. As a CEO, I'm trying to create a lot of time consensus in the company, and I have a lot of problems to deal with. And deciding not to use scale would probably create a war of my engineers, so we're going to stick to it. For AI, Gale Whip's clearly the top partner in the industry and we're super excited to be working with them.",
